metadata.name: Ancestral Memory
metadata.description:
Ancestral Memory -  Archetypal Meditation #1

There is a memory deep in our bones, passed on since life first gave rise to life. It flows, it gives and it takes. Blossoming, blooming and dancing - this piece imagines the experience of eternity embedded in Ancestral Memory. 

The endless being calls forth the endless story - spun line by line with the fine silk of genetic code into a web of infinite complexity, forever iterating across time and space. 

What story will you leave etched on your link of the chain?

ArtBreeder, ProsePainter
